Includes: Phase detection, combo amplification, VIE action mapping,
research patch outputs (style markers, data sufficiency, evidence governance,
coaching rubric, retention policy), and romance false-positive guardrails.
Fail-closed: any API failure returns degraded=True, risk_score=100.
"""

